# websocket-pool.word — the WebSocket pool as a being; one connection matter per live socket, its
# act-chain the connection log. Descends from able.word.

A websocket-pool is an able.
A websocket-pool can see connections.
A websocket-pool can see http-stats.
A websocket-pool can do make.
A websocket-pool can do set-matter.
A websocket-pool can do end-matter.
A websocket-pool needs scripted cognition.
